   Technology &amp; Medicine:
   Control Data Head
   Offers an Apology
   For Prodigal Past
   ---
   Perlman Vows End to Tilting
   At Quixotic Ventures
   Like Windmill Farms
   ----
   By Richard Gibson
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/03/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
